      "title": "Joe Biden says the symptoms are mild",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "US President Joe Biden said he was experiencing mild symptoms after testing positive for Covid-19 on July 21.",
        "However, he has further stated that he is fine and is spending time in isolation as per medical advice."
